#include<bits/stdc++.h>
using namespace std;
int N,created,len;string str;
struct node
{
    bool leaf;
    struct node* ar[26];
}*root,*temp;
int main()
{
    ios_base::sync_with_stdio(false);cin.tie(NULL);
    cin>>N;root=new node();
    for(int i=0;i<N;i++)
    {
        cin>>str;temp=root;created=0;len=str.length();
        for(int k=0;k<len;k++)
        {
            if(temp->ar[str[k]-'a']==NULL)
            {temp->ar[str[k]-'a']=new node();created=1;}
            temp=temp->ar[str[k]-'a'];
            if(temp->leaf&&k!=len-1){cout<<"vulnerable";return 0;}
            if(k==len-1)
            {
                temp->leaf=true;if(!created){cout<<"vulnerable";return 0;}
            }
        }
    }
    cout<<"non vulnerable";
    return 0;
}
